				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">Not to be confused with <a href="Scottish_English" title="Scottish English">Scottish English</a>&#160;or <a href="Scottish_Gaelic" title="Scottish Gaelic">Scottish Gaelic</a>.</div>
<table class="infobox" cellspacing="3" style="border-spacing: 3px; width:22em;">
